metadata.name: Mercury
metadata.description:
Mercury by Fahfahs is based on uwucrew #3209 and is the first of nine Systema Solaris auctions!

Systema Solaris is uwucrew's first Artist Megacollab, where 9 artists each create a Solar System themed uwucrew derivative piece to be auctioned off!

All bidders will also receive the corresponding Mercury stamp after the last auction ends.
